title: Is We Dumb? | High Kick. Hitman. Crocs. Reward Box.
description:
Remember that time you tried to hire a hitman to kill your husband, but you went to the most obvious fake website ever to hire them and framed yourself? Let's talk about that, drug smugglers who called the cops on themselves,  refusing to serve non-locals food, your brain cells meeting around a conference table, and more on today's episode of Is We Dumb?!  

 

New episodes every Wednesday at 12pm PST
